These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rabbit##7
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | chinchilla | rabbit | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, garlic, broccoli, lime
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating blueberry##7
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating garlic and the person eating lime##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | blueberry | lime | broccoli | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, tomato, potato, watermelon
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person eating tomato##7
3. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | mango | tomato | watermelon | potato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, trike, car
1. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the car and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | subway | car | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, romance, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching spy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | thriller | musical | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, indonesian, american
1. the spanish is somewhere between the american and the chinese##7
2. the indonesian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the american##3
4. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian | spanish | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, coffee, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking soy-milk##7
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking cola##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | coffee | cola |

