2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching zombie movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | disaster | thriller | zombie |

