.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | snowmobile | quad-bike | car |

